1
00:00:01,170 --> 00:00:03,610
(Episode 73)

2
00:00:05,240 --> 00:00:06,480
(Genos Gene Examination Center)

3
00:00:06,540 --> 00:00:07,550
Thank you.

4
00:00:11,850 --> 00:00:12,850
Mom. Mom!

5
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:20,860
You used Chae Hwa Young and Ma Seo Rin's
toothbrushes for the DNA test, right?

6
00:00:21,090 --> 00:00:22,730
Of course. You saw for yourself.

7
00:00:23,030 --> 00:00:24,560
Okay. Let's see what it says.

8
00:00:26,830 --> 00:00:29,270
Chae Hwa Young, you're finished.

9
00:00:31,770 --> 00:00:33,670
(Genos Gene Examination Center)

10
00:00:33,740 --> 00:00:34,740
- One...
- One...

11
00:00:35,540 --> 00:00:36,540
- Two...
- Two...

12
00:00:37,210 --> 00:00:38,210
- Three!
- Three!

13
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:42,480
(Ma Seo Rin and Chae Hwa Young
are mother and daughter)

14
00:00:42,580 --> 00:00:46,480
What? Wait.
It says they're mother and daughter?

15
00:00:47,690 --> 00:00:48,690
How can this be?

16
00:00:49,390 --> 00:00:52,720
It says Seo Rin and Chae Hwa Young
are mother and daughter.

17
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:54,630
I know. This is so weird.

18
00:00:55,330 --> 00:00:57,800
But I'm positive I saw Oh Jang Mi,
who looked like a twin.

19
00:00:57,930 --> 00:01:01,900
Please. What did you really see?
You saw a look-alike and jumped the gun.

20
00:01:01,970 --> 00:01:06,370
- That's not it! I swear, she has a twin!
- But then this doesn't make any sense.

21
00:01:08,570 --> 00:01:10,070
So let's say they are twins.

22
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:13,280
But that would mean
they're both Chae Hwa Young's daughters.

23
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:17,020
Wait, then
why would she raise them separately?

24
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:19,020
Wow, this is getting really confusing.

25
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:23,890
Gosh, this means we have nothing
to blackmail that woman with.

26
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,260
Gosh, this is so frustrating!

27
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:27,330
(Explanation of Results)

28
00:01:27,390 --> 00:01:29,230
(Maternity is 99.99% probable.
It confirms a mother-daughter link.)

29
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:42,540
What did you say?

30
00:01:42,810 --> 00:01:46,410
Jin Hong Ju ordered a DNA test
on me and Seo Rin?

31
00:01:46,850 --> 00:01:49,410
Yes, the results are expected
to arrive today.

32
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,480
Those two have some serious nerve.

33
00:01:53,050 --> 00:01:54,320
We need to act fast.

34
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:56,790
We have to get ahead of this
before the results arrive.

35
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:59,960
Yes, CEO Chae. I've prepared everything
and have just arrived at the house.

36
00:02:00,490 --> 00:02:02,890
Good. Handle it without any mistakes.

37
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:06,600
Thank you.

38
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:19,080
(OK Quick Service)

39
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:26,220
(A maternal link between Ma Seo Rin
and Chae Hwa Young is not established.)

40
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:36,690
No matter how much you two try
to mess with me, you'll never win.

41
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,240
- Yes, CEO Chae.
- Thank you, Kang Hyuk.

42
00:02:47,570 --> 00:02:50,680
I can finally breathe a sigh of relief,
all thanks to you acting first.

43
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:53,280
I don't know what I would've done
without you.

44
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:54,880
I'm just glad everything worked out.

45
00:02:55,250 --> 00:02:59,880
Still, Yeom San Wol and Jin Hong Ju.
Those two are a constant nuisance.

46
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:04,790
They're going to keep being suspicious,
so I need to shut them up for good.

47
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:08,190
So they can never run their mouths
about some twins again.

48
00:03:09,890 --> 00:03:11,030
I have a way.

49
00:03:12,930 --> 00:03:13,930
You do?

50
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:19,770
I think this baby photo is from Wonpyeong.
I'm going to look for the studio.

51
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:20,940
In Wonpyeong?

52
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:24,880
That photo looks like it's ages old.
You think the studio's still there?

53
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,880
Find out first,
and then let's go together.

54
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:30,750
I think I got a text.
See you at the office, honey.

55
00:03:33,250 --> 00:03:34,290
This is Kang Jun Ho.

56
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:38,490
I have something to discuss,
so let's meet in my office when you're in.

57
00:03:40,490 --> 00:03:41,760
What could he want to talk about?

58
00:03:42,790 --> 00:03:44,060
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

59
00:03:44,230 --> 00:03:48,100
Hello. This is Suk Hee's Side Dishes.
You ordered from us before.

60
00:03:48,270 --> 00:03:50,900
I know, I know. Of course I do.

61
00:03:52,370 --> 00:03:55,510
My dear Tae Pyung, what's the occasion
for you to be calling me?

62
00:03:55,570 --> 00:03:57,640
I was just wondering
why you haven't stopped by lately.

63
00:03:58,010 --> 00:03:59,880
I was a little worried
something might have happened.

64
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:04,180
Oh my, you were worried about me?
I'm so touched, Tae Pyung.

65
00:04:04,780 --> 00:04:06,080
So you missed me.

66
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:07,920
Mom.

67
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:15,790
I made some healthy and delicious dishes,
so please stop by when you have time.

68
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:19,330
I will.
I'll make time even if I don't have any.

69
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:24,270
No matter how busy I am, I'll rush over,
so have them ready for me, Tae Pyung.

70
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:28,110
I was just curious about something.

71
00:04:28,910 --> 00:04:30,680
How did you know my name?

72
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:35,710
Please. How could I not know your name?
It'd be stranger if I didn't.

73
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:38,650
And one more thing, Tae Pyung.

74
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:43,150
My name isn't "ma'am." It's Yeom San Wol.

75
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:47,830
From now on, don't call me ma'am.
Just call me San Wol.

76
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:48,960
Got it?

77
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,900
All right, then.
I'll get your side dishes ready.

78
00:04:58,640 --> 00:05:01,710
Is she on something? What is with her?

79
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:03,680
So creepy. Seriously.

80
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:09,050
Mom, what's this "Tae Pyung"
all of a sudden?

81
00:05:09,650 --> 00:05:11,780
Don't tell me you have a thing
for that guy.

82
00:05:12,250 --> 00:05:15,420
- Honestly, what are you talking about?
- Right?

83
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:19,160
That would be an insane story.
Just the thought of it creeps me out.

84
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:21,360
Stop with the nonsense.

85
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:24,530
Just come up with a plan
to investigate those twins.

86
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:29,230
We can't just give up a golden opportunity
to screw over Chae Hwa Young.

87
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:33,740
They must be Chae Hwa Young's daughters.
We need to learn why she only raised one.

88
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:35,540
My point exactly.

89
00:05:35,810 --> 00:05:39,540
To do that, we need to get friendly
with Oh Jang Mi's family, don't we?

90
00:05:40,180 --> 00:05:42,510
And it turns out, Tae Pyung is
Oh Jang Mi's older brother.

91
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:45,880
That's why I'm meeting with him now...

92
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:48,290
to do a little digging.

93
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:52,620
- Smart, right?
- Then why are you all dolled up, Mom?

94
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:55,360
What, you'd rather I go around
looking like I'm sick?

95
00:05:55,690 --> 00:05:57,830
Just be careful not to give the Chairman
anything to use against you.

96
00:05:57,960 --> 00:06:00,870
You know we're a package deal, right?

97
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:06,870
Please, have some.

98
00:06:08,410 --> 00:06:11,180
That's right. I can't be CEO Chae's son.

99
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,540
I have to be wrong about this.

100
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,210
What did you want to talk about?

101
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,850
I'll get straight to the point.

102
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:19,020
Let's go out.

103
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:22,990
- What?
- I'm interested in you, Director Ma.

104
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:27,590
Wait, you were just calling me a stalker,
and now this? What are you talking about?

105
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:29,930
It's like you've had
a sudden change of heart.

106
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:32,500
You're right.
I did have a change of heart.

107
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,200
I've become more interested in you,

108
00:06:35,470 --> 00:06:38,170
and more than anything,
I've become curious about you.

109
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:39,940
That's not going to work.

110
00:06:44,210 --> 00:06:45,880
I mean... No.

111
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:48,210
I'm not interested in you anymore.

112
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:51,950
Aren't you going to ask why?

113
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:55,090
- Is it because of my brother?
- Bingo.

114
00:06:55,690 --> 00:06:59,120
Plus, I'm more into new people.
And another thing,

115
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:02,090
I lose interest
when someone says they like me.

116
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:06,460
There's no thrill of the chase, you know?
Once you've conquered the mountain,

117
00:07:06,930 --> 00:07:08,070
it's no fun anymore.

118
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:11,200
So you're that certain I like you?

119
00:07:12,700 --> 00:07:15,670
- Am I wrong?
- Think whatever you like.

120
00:07:16,470 --> 00:07:19,780
My plan is to start dating you now,

121
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:23,610
- and then marry you very soon.
- What? Marry me?

122
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:25,020
You've got to be kidding me!

123
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:27,250
Of course,
your opinion on the matter is irrelevant.

124
00:07:27,990 --> 00:07:29,790
Because the woman I'm going to marry
is Seo Rin.

125
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,860
Look here, Kang Jun Ho.

126
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:36,890
The person I like is your brother,
Kang Baek Ho! Didn't you hear me?

127
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:38,800
Like Baek Ho all you want.

128
00:07:39,530 --> 00:07:42,970
But you're going to marry me.
I'll make sure of that.

129
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:48,510
What, did you suddenly get ambitious?
Why are you doing this?

130
00:07:54,450 --> 00:07:57,110
Baek Ho. Can I see you
for a moment this evening?

131
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:58,450
There's something I need to talk about.

132
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,590
I'm sorry, Team Leader Jin.
I have a family matter to attend to.

133
00:08:02,020 --> 00:08:03,350
Whatever it is, just tell me now.

134
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:06,520
This isn't really the place
to talk about it, though.

135
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:10,060
What?

136
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:12,430
What's this, you two?

137
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:14,230
CEO Chae.

138
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,830
Team Leader Jin.

139
00:08:16,130 --> 00:08:18,540
Did you bring Lawyer Kang to the company
just to have an office romance?

140
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,970
Watch your mouth, CEO Chae.

141
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:22,310
What are you talking about?
Who's having a romance?

142
00:08:23,370 --> 00:08:24,380
Oh, dear.

143
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:28,610
So, you're just pining after him
without even confessing, Team Leader Jin?

144
00:08:29,650 --> 00:08:31,880
When Lawyer Kang is in love
with someone else,

145
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:33,850
so much for your undying devotion.

146
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:36,950
- CEO Chae.
- This is none of your business.

147
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:38,720
Now you're just pathetic.

148
00:08:39,190 --> 00:08:41,930
Besides,
the sleeping princess has finally awoken,

149
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:45,260
all your efforts to win over Lawyer Kang
will be for nothing.

150
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:47,400
Snap out of it, Team Leader Jin.

151
00:08:48,970 --> 00:08:51,170
Lawyer Kang Baek Ho,
I'd like a word with you.

152
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:54,870
Fine. I also have something to say to you,
so this is perfect.

153
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:08,590
You've been busy,
haven't you, Kang Baek Ho?

154
00:09:09,050 --> 00:09:12,760
Getting Oh Jang Mi discharged
and plotting to sabotage me.

155
00:09:13,590 --> 00:09:17,300
And all while pretending to be my lawyer.
You've got some nerve.

156
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:20,300
- I don't know what you're talking about.
- So you're going to play dumb?

157
00:09:21,330 --> 00:09:24,640
- I guess you have to say that.
- More importantly,

158
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,970
I'm talking about Jang Mi's father,
the late Mr. Oh Bok Gil.

159
00:09:28,310 --> 00:09:30,910
Explain to me
why my father is involved in that case.

160
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:34,680
Was it your plan from the beginning
to have my father hit him with a car?

161
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:35,910
What?

162
00:09:36,310 --> 00:09:37,450
How dare you say that?

163
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:39,220
How could you think of using my father...

164
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,120
in the death of Jang Mi's father?

165
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:43,050
Are you even human?

166
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:46,760
- Using my father for your crime.
- Shut it!

167
00:09:47,090 --> 00:09:50,960
- "Using" him?
- So you have no intention of confessing.

168
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:54,170
- Then should I lay it all out for you?
- Watch your mouth, Kang Baek Ho.

169
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:58,500
The more recklessly you lash out
like this,

170
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:01,410
you should know things will only get worse
for you and Oh Jang Mi.

171
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:04,440
So you're just going to keep denying it,
thinking I have no hard evidence?

172
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:09,710
- We'll see how long you can keep that up.
- Fine. Let's see you try.

173
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:14,220
Where's Oh Jang Mi? I said, where is she?

174
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:19,320
- Why would I have to tell you that?
- Where did you hide her? Tell me!

175
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:22,330
CEO Chae Hwa Young,
you listen to me very carefully.

176
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:26,560
From now on, stay away from Oh Jang Mi.
And don't even try to find her.

177
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:29,170
Next time, it won't just be a warning.

178
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:38,010
Oh Jang Mi and Kang Baek Ho.

179
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:40,280
You think I'm going to let you two
get away with this?

180
00:10:41,210 --> 00:10:42,310
Just you wait.

181
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:57,900
When Lawyer Kang is in love
with someone else,

182
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:59,560
so much for your undying devotion.

183
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,100
Now you're just pathetic.

184
00:11:02,970 --> 00:11:04,670
Gosh, how humiliating.

185
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,870
Something's off about CEO Chae.

186
00:11:07,370 --> 00:11:11,510
If Oh Jang Mi and Seo Rin are twins,
then Oh Jang Mi must be her daughter too.

187
00:11:12,210 --> 00:11:13,910
But she talks about her
as if she's a total stranger.

188
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,250
Here you go.

189
00:11:17,650 --> 00:11:19,250
Oh my, you gave me so much!

190
00:11:19,650 --> 00:11:21,650
Come on, you're one of our best customers.

191
00:11:22,690 --> 00:11:24,720
But that looks heavy.

192
00:11:25,260 --> 00:11:27,390
Would you like me to deliver it
on my motorcycle?

193
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:30,560
Perfect timing.
I just sent my driver home.

194
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:34,070
Think you can give me a ride
on that bike of yours, Tae Pyung?

195
00:11:34,830 --> 00:11:35,830
Excuse me?

196
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:41,610
Wouldn't you be uncomfortable?

197
00:11:42,210 --> 00:11:45,010
Uncomfortable? Please. Back in my day,

198
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:47,380
I had no problem holding on
to a guy on his bike.

199
00:11:49,310 --> 00:11:50,850
In that case, shall we go?

200
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:52,950
Okay.

201
00:11:56,950 --> 00:11:57,960
Mom.

202
00:11:58,620 --> 00:11:59,920
I'm heading out for a delivery.

203
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:11,640
- I'm home, honey.
- Oh my, what's that?

204
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:18,110
I realized it's been a long time
since I bought you a bouquet of flowers.

205
00:12:18,310 --> 00:12:19,310
Here, take it.

206
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:27,220
You like them that much?

207
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:29,990
Of course I do.

208
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:34,830
I must be the only wife my age
who gets bouquets from her husband.

209
00:12:35,890 --> 00:12:37,230
My wonderful husband.

210
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:41,130
This should stop her from suspecting me
again, right?

211
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:44,370
I wonder if Hwa Young would like
a bouquet, too.

212
00:12:45,970 --> 00:12:48,040
I can't believe I ever suspected
a husband like you.

213
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:50,980
I don't know what got into me.

214
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:53,080
I'm so sorry, honey.

215
00:12:53,580 --> 00:12:56,010
It's okay. Don't worry about it.

216
00:13:05,220 --> 00:13:06,220
Ma'am.

217
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,230
You know Seo Rin, right?

218
00:13:09,530 --> 00:13:10,630
That's Tok Hee.

219
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:12,560
Tok Hee?

220
00:13:13,660 --> 00:13:17,100
Anyway, the Oh Jang Mi
who looks just like her.

221
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,670
Is she your daughter, by any chance?

222
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,940
Jang Mi is Suk Hee's daughter.

223
00:13:22,370 --> 00:13:25,140
Tok Hee is Suk Hee's daughter too.
Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

224
00:13:26,310 --> 00:13:27,510
Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

225
00:13:30,010 --> 00:13:31,120
I'm not sure I believe you.

226
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:33,920
Don't you have a picture of Oh Jang Mi?

227
00:13:38,060 --> 00:13:42,060
Look at this. This is my Jang Mi.
Jang Mi is so pretty.

228
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,900
Where is Jang Mi's room?

229
00:13:47,830 --> 00:13:50,970
Jang Mi's not here. Not here now.
Jang Mi's not here.

230
00:13:54,370 --> 00:13:55,410
Gosh.

231
00:13:56,570 --> 00:13:58,340
Show me a picture.

232
00:13:58,340 --> 00:14:00,110
That's the only way I'll believe
this "Ok Hee Tok Hee" business.

233
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:02,680
Ok Hee and Tok Hee are
Suk Hee's daughters.

234
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:05,550
Here.

235
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,590
Here.

236
00:14:11,290 --> 00:14:12,460
Here it is.

237
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:16,830
That's my Jang Mi. Jang Mi's pretty.
Jang Mi is Suk Hee's daughter.

238
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:20,360
I see that now. They really are twins.

239
00:14:28,710 --> 00:14:30,040
Ma'am.

240
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:33,610
You said you had something to tell me
about my Jang Mi,

241
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,350
so why did you bring me here?

242
00:14:35,650 --> 00:14:37,210
- Boss.
- Yes?

243
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:39,180
- A bottle of soju, please.
- Right away.

244
00:14:40,450 --> 00:14:44,420
I can't possibly tell you
this shocking secret...

245
00:14:44,690 --> 00:14:46,420
without having a drink first.

246
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:50,330
What is this lady up to?

247
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:52,630
What could she possibly know
about my Jang Mi?

248
00:14:57,230 --> 00:14:58,540
Mom, look at this.

249
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:03,840
I took this at Oh Jang Mi's house.
Jang Mi and Seo Rin really are twins.

250
00:15:03,940 --> 00:15:06,780
So they really are twins. Oh my goodness.

251
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:09,080
Seeing the proof just makes my head
spin even more.

252
00:15:09,610 --> 00:15:10,710
Excuse me?

253
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:19,390
Just drink up. For now.

254
00:15:19,890 --> 00:15:22,760
Wait, what do you mean,
"they really are twins?"

255
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:24,600
I don't understand what you mean.

256
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:29,600
This is Oh Jang Mi, right?

257
00:15:30,270 --> 00:15:34,610
I know all about it.
That Oh Jang Mi and Ma Seo Rin are twins.

258
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:38,540
Come on, twins?
They must just be look-alikes.

259
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:42,710
Jang Mi's mother is my mom,
and Ma Seo Rin's mother is CEO Chae.

260
00:15:43,980 --> 00:15:45,820
Look-alikes, you say?

261
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:48,590
Of course. There's no way
they could be twins.

262
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:53,790
Ma'am, do you have any idea
how many look-alikes are in the world?

263
00:15:54,730 --> 00:15:59,200
Here, let me pour you a drink.
Let's not jump to such wild conclusions.

264
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:00,660
Here you go.

265
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:04,900
Oh man, this is bad.

266
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:08,040
I should get going.

267
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:11,380
My deliveries are backed up,
and they're blowing up my phone.

268
00:16:11,910 --> 00:16:13,280
Please, excuse me.

269
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:15,010
Wait, hold on.

270
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:22,420
Darn it. I hoped we could have a drink
and get into a more serious discussion.

271
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:24,320
And he just ran off like that.

272
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:26,920
What a shame.

273
00:16:31,300 --> 00:16:32,300
Excuse me.

274
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,130
It looks like you've been stood up.

275
00:16:36,230 --> 00:16:37,800
Would you care to have a drink with me?

276
00:16:38,900 --> 00:16:40,100
Stood up? Don't be ridiculous.

277
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:41,940
I got stood up too.

278
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:44,980
My fiancee said she'd be here,
but she's a no-show.

279
00:16:45,380 --> 00:16:47,610
Is that so?

280
00:16:48,650 --> 00:16:51,280
Here, you can just put this bottle
on hold for me.

281
00:16:52,350 --> 00:16:54,820
Tonight's on me.

282
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:57,250
After all, it must be fate
that we met like this.

283
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:02,590
Well then, cheers.

284
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:09,700
Since you're buying,
I guess I'll have one.

285
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:14,910
But for the record, I wasn't stood up.
I was here on business.

286
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:17,410
My situation is nothing like yours.

287
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:18,780
Right.

288
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:20,610
This is so frustrating.

289
00:17:21,580 --> 00:17:22,580
Go on, drink up.

290
00:17:23,450 --> 00:17:24,450
Unbelievable.

291
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:35,260
One more?

292
00:17:36,730 --> 00:17:37,760
Here you go.

293
00:17:45,670 --> 00:17:46,670
Yes.

294
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:51,180
Target neutralized.

295
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,140
Right. Good work.

296
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,850
And make sure you clean up properly.

297
00:17:56,950 --> 00:17:59,850
This should be enough
to keep Yeom San Wol's mouth shut, right?

298
00:18:00,220 --> 00:18:01,220
Yes.

299
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:04,820
She won't dare say a word
or Chairman Ma will kick her out.

300
00:18:10,090 --> 00:18:13,860
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

301
00:18:17,730 --> 00:18:19,670
There's no way you're my mother.

302
00:18:22,910 --> 00:18:23,970
You're here.

303
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:27,810
General Manager Kang, it's past
quitting time, and you're still working.

304
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:31,080
- You should take care of yourself.
- That's rich.

305
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,580
I just can't get used to
this side of you, CEO Chae.

306
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:35,120
Of all the things,

307
00:18:35,390 --> 00:18:37,860
to hear you of all people tell me
to take care of myself.

308
00:18:39,190 --> 00:18:40,190
General Manager Kang.

309
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:43,590
I feel like I've apologized to you
countless times,

310
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:47,130
but it seems you're still upset with me.

311
00:18:53,470 --> 00:18:57,140
I wanted to discuss the hotel's convention
for the latter half of the year.

312
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:01,680
But...

313
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:05,880
you don't seem to be yourself.
I'm concerned.

314
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:07,620
Is something wrong?

315
00:19:08,050 --> 00:19:09,550
There's always something wrong.

316
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:12,020
But you never cease to amaze me.

317
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:16,360
Since when have you ever cared
about an employee's feelings?

318
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:20,900
To think I never realized
what a considerate CEO you are...

319
00:19:21,470 --> 00:19:22,470
My apologies.

320
00:19:24,430 --> 00:19:26,600
You're the brains of our company,
General Manager Kang.

321
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:29,940
If anything's wrong, just tell me.
I'll help.

322
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:32,010
Because of a piece of trash
that isn't even human,

323
00:19:32,610 --> 00:19:35,380
I feel like my whole life has been
a wretched, unfair tragedy.

324
00:19:36,250 --> 00:19:39,780
It's not something you can help me with,
so please don't concern yourself.

325
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:43,850
The kind of life you've lived...

326
00:19:45,220 --> 00:19:46,860
I can't even begin to imagine.

327
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:51,260
The woman who calls herself my mother...

328
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:55,600
abandoned her own newborn child
without a second thought.

329
00:19:57,970 --> 00:19:59,800
Then she went on to live a happy life,
as if to mock me.

330
00:20:01,170 --> 00:20:03,070
For some reason,
I heard she was looking for me.

331
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:07,740
I was curious about why she abandoned me,
so I tried to meet her,

332
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:11,320
but she said it wasn't a good time
and to leave her alone.

333
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:15,750
She abandoned me twice.

334
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:18,760
Never again...

335
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:22,730
Never again will I look for that woman.

336
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:28,330
No. In fact, to me, that woman
never even existed in the first place.

337
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:30,630
So there's no reason for me
to be sad about it now, is there?

338
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:34,100
I'm sorry.

339
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:37,170
For telling you all this
when it has nothing to do with you.

340
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:40,140
Not at all.

341
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:42,980
Thank you for opening up to me.

342
00:20:44,210 --> 00:20:45,780
But I'm worried.

343
00:20:46,780 --> 00:20:50,050
If you have that much resentment built up
toward your mother,

344
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:53,720
you must be in a lot of pain yourself.
That's what worries me.

345
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:56,730
You don't need
to worry about that, CEO Chae.

346
00:20:57,330 --> 00:20:58,930
Hating someone...

347
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:00,930
only makes you suffer more in the end.

348
00:21:02,130 --> 00:21:03,630
You might not realize it yourself,

349
00:21:04,530 --> 00:21:07,140
but the poisoned arrow of hatred
pierces your own heart,

350
00:21:07,670 --> 00:21:09,670
and the venom inevitably spreads
throughout your body.

351
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,310
I guess that comes with being the CEO.

352
00:21:14,140 --> 00:21:15,480
You seem to know that all too well.

353
00:21:16,380 --> 00:21:19,950
I suppose you must have experience
hating someone that much yourself.

354
00:21:20,350 --> 00:21:21,350
What?

355
00:21:22,090 --> 00:21:23,120
Me?

356
00:21:24,660 --> 00:21:25,660
I guess you're right.

357
00:21:27,190 --> 00:21:28,190
There is someone...

358
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,430
that I hate very much.

359
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:35,330
People rarely know themselves.

360
00:21:36,230 --> 00:21:38,440
They're always lenient on themselves.

361
00:21:39,570 --> 00:21:43,270
They're a monster riddled with
greed and hypocrisy on the inside,

362
00:21:44,170 --> 00:21:45,640
but they pretend to be a benevolent,

363
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:49,310
conscientious angel on the outside.
Isn't that what people are?

364
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:54,620
You're not talking about me, are you?

365
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:59,120
Why would I say something like that
about you?

366
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:03,060
I'm talking about my so-called mother,
who abandoned me.

367
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:25,080
Jun Ho, what's gotten into you?
You're drinking.

368
00:22:26,750 --> 00:22:28,220
You must have something to tell me, right?

369
00:22:28,990 --> 00:22:30,220
So, what is it?

370
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:33,660
I'm going to marry Director Ma Seo Rin.

371
00:22:35,290 --> 00:22:36,290
What?

372
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:38,960
- You're marrying who?
- Seo Rin.

373
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:42,300
Wait, Jun Ho,
you said you didn't like Seo Rin.

374
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:45,870
She's changed.
Maybe it's because she lost her memory,

375
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:47,940
but she's become a warmer person.

376
00:22:48,570 --> 00:22:52,180
- And now you're in love?
- Listen.

377
00:22:53,340 --> 00:22:54,880
Stop flirting with Seo Rin.

378
00:22:56,050 --> 00:22:58,620
You're in love with that woman,
Oh Jang Mi, right?

379
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:01,490
Weren't you just
at her hospital room today?

380
00:23:02,450 --> 00:23:04,760
So why do you keep hitting on Seo Rin?

381
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:07,160
I didn't think you were that kind of guy.

382
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:12,030
- It's just...
- It seems Seo Rin likes you,

383
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:16,030
but it's only temporary.
So don't lead her on.

384
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:20,870
- Because I'm going to marry her.
- Wait, has Seo Rin agreed to marry you?

385
00:23:21,340 --> 00:23:22,570
That's not the case, is it?

386
00:23:23,810 --> 00:23:24,980
I've made myself clear.

387
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:27,940
Seo Rin is going to be
your future sister-in-law.

388
00:23:28,710 --> 00:23:29,710
Don't you forget it.

389
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:41,630
Gosh, how did things get so twisted?
This is driving me nuts.

390
00:23:42,190 --> 00:23:45,460
Why did Jun Ho have to
suddenly fall for her?

391
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:47,400
And I can't even tell him the truth.

392
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:57,810
So, Mrs. Yeom isn't here yet?

393
00:23:59,210 --> 00:24:00,680
Where on earth could she be?

394
00:24:01,310 --> 00:24:04,310
I'll try calling my mom again.

395
00:24:22,700 --> 00:24:23,970
Where am I?

396
00:24:28,810 --> 00:24:29,810
Gosh, my head hurts.

397
00:24:35,910 --> 00:24:36,980
Oh my gosh!

398
00:24:37,550 --> 00:24:38,580
What in the world is this?

399
00:24:41,480 --> 00:24:42,720
Oh no, what do I do?

400
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:48,860
They came out well.

401
00:24:49,130 --> 00:24:51,030
Print the photos
and send a copy to the house,

402
00:24:51,390 --> 00:24:52,530
and send one to Hong Ju too.

403
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:56,270
If she has half a brain,
she'll get the message immediately.

404
00:24:56,430 --> 00:24:57,430
Yes, ma'am.

405
00:25:07,410 --> 00:25:08,410
Mom!

406
00:25:17,850 --> 00:25:19,090
My goodness.

407
00:25:19,820 --> 00:25:22,660
Looks like Yeom San Wol
is having a full-blown affair.

408
00:25:23,230 --> 00:25:27,330
- Mom, are you crazy?
- What if the Chairman finds out?

409
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:30,570
The Chairman can never find out.
Absolutely not.

410
00:25:30,770 --> 00:25:33,500
Do you know what I went through
to get to this position?

411
00:25:34,700 --> 00:25:37,110
No. He can never, ever find out.

412
00:25:37,810 --> 00:25:42,050
- Mom, your phone's ringing. Answer it.
- What? Right.

413
00:25:46,080 --> 00:25:47,080
Hello?

414
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:51,220
- This is Yeom San Wol speaking.
- Hey there. Did you sleep well?

415
00:25:54,290 --> 00:25:57,390
- Who's this?
- Gosh, that's cold.

416
00:25:57,960 --> 00:26:01,260
Forgetting my voice already,
after the night we had?

417
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,800
The night we had?

418
00:26:03,100 --> 00:26:04,940
I even sent you a photo to remember me by.

419
00:26:05,370 --> 00:26:08,040
- I guess you haven't seen it yet.
- A photo?

420
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:10,440
It can't be...

421
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:16,980
Oh my gosh!

422
00:26:17,450 --> 00:26:19,550
Oh my! What is that?

423
00:26:25,790 --> 00:26:28,590
- Who is it?
- The Chairman is looking for you.

424
00:26:30,130 --> 00:26:32,200
Tell him I'll be right there.

425
00:26:32,430 --> 00:26:35,030
Gosh, what are you doing in there
with the door locked?

426
00:26:35,130 --> 00:26:38,400
How dare you talk back to me?
I said I'll be right there!

427
00:26:38,670 --> 00:26:39,970
Now, go away!

428
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:47,010
- Are you Ms. Oh Jang Mi's guardian?
- Yes.

429
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:51,480
Ms. Oh Jang Mi just moved her finger.
It looks like she's starting to wake up.

430
00:26:51,850 --> 00:26:54,580
Really?
Okay, I understand. I'll be right there.

431
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:00,660
Jang Mi.

432
00:27:02,630 --> 00:27:05,030
- Jang Mi, where are you?
- I'm out. Why?

433
00:27:05,330 --> 00:27:06,430
Out where?

434
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:08,570
You need to come with me somewhere.
Right now.

435
00:27:17,570 --> 00:27:19,880
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

436
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:25,380
CEO Chae, it looks like Kang Baek Ho
is on his way to meet Oh Jang Mi.

437
00:27:25,820 --> 00:27:27,950
Really? Get the car. Now.

438
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:47,240
Tail them. Quickly!

439
00:28:38,190 --> 00:28:39,820
(The First Man)

440
00:28:39,890 --> 00:28:44,360
What do you think will happen
when the Chairman finds out she's a twin?

441
00:28:44,430 --> 00:28:48,570
How does that sound, Yeom San Wol?
It's you who'll be kicked out.

442
00:28:48,730 --> 00:28:52,400
Is this the Private Detective Agency?
I need a report on CEO Chae Hwa Young.

443
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:55,840
- You can stop the investigation now.
- Please, just forgive me.

444
00:28:56,210 --> 00:28:58,010
I will never forgive you.

445
00:28:58,410 --> 00:29:00,910
No matter what, you are my son...

446
00:29:01,010 --> 00:29:03,550
and Seo Rin is not my biological daughter.

447
00:29:03,980 --> 00:29:07,080
So then,
Chae Hwa Young's son is Kang Jun Ho?

448
00:29:08,320 --> 00:29:10,320
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
